<div class="title">A Total Flop</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca (B. caapi & P. viridis)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Alforn&Exact=1">Alforn</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Alforn. "A Total Flop: An Experience with Ayahuasca (B. caapi & P. viridis) (exp58296)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 13, 2007. erowid.org/exp/58296</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
